dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Frank Sanchez. May I have your name, please?
Hi, my name is Ann Butler.
Nice to meet you, Ann. Can you please provide me with the first three digits of your policy number?
Thank you. And for security verification, could you now provide me with the ZIP code associated with your policy address?
The ZIP code is nine zero one two three.
Great, thank you for verifying your information, Ann. How can I assist you today regarding your policy or any other inquiries?
I would like to check the status of a claim I filed last week.
Of course, I can help with that. Thank you for your time, Ann. I will look into it and get back to you shortly.
Thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. Have a great day! Goodbye.
